      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideally suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The exterior has sustained significant damage, including heavy rusting on the wheel arches and several large dents along the passenger side. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to invest considerable time and resources to get this car back on the road.",
