      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It runs beautifully and still looks sharp. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, comfy car that won't break the bank, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
