    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine. This high-revving powerplant maintains excellent compression and features a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with precision, delivering power to the rear wheels via the factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings, and the subframe has been inspected for structural integrity. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering the tactile feedback and linear power delivery that defines this era of M-division engineering.",
