      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust, having recently undergone a full inspection, brake pad replacement, and synthetic oil service. The engine pulls smoothly without hesitation, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. It has been garage-kept by a non-smoker and comes with a documented service history. This is a reliable, attractive car that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
